  namespace ForestCompositionLaw
    /-!
    Given any birds `A`, `B`, `C`, the bird `C` is said to *compose*
    `A` with `B` if for every bird `x`, the following condition holds
                      (C ‚óĀ x) = (A ‚óĀ (B ‚óĀ x))

